DESCRIPTION:Join us on Wednesday\, June 17\, from 4-7 PM at Whispering Vine South Creek for a Domaine Roland Lavantureux tasting featuring Chablis\, Petit Chablis\, Bourgogne Tonnerre and Bourgogne Epineuil.\nTasting Fee: $35 per person (Buy a tasting bottle and your fee is refunded.)\nFeatured Wines:\n- Domaine Roland Lavantureux Chablis Vaux Carres 2023 - $39.99 - Citrus\, green apple\, oyster shell and chalk with a precise\, saline finish.\n- Roland Lavantureux Petit Chablis 2023 - $34.99 - Floral\, flinty and fresh\, with citrus\, apple and limestone-driven lift.\n- Roland Lavantureux Bourgogne Tonnerre 2022 - $35.99 - Orchard fruit\, oyster-shell minerality and a rounder Bourgogne Blanc texture.\n- Roland Lavantureux Bourgogne Epineuil 2022 - $39.99 - Crunchy red fruit\, floral lift\, peppery spice and bright Pinot Noir finesse.\nCome taste through Domaine Roland Lavantureux and find your favorite bottle. Buy a tasting bottle and your fee is refunded.
LOCATION:85 Foothill Rd Ste 1 Reno\, NV 89511
SUMMARY:Roland Lavantureux Tasting
END:VEVENT
END:VCALENDAR